                        <locus target="#66r"/> 
                        <desc>Virgin Mary and the Child with the archangels Michael and
                           Gabriel.</desc>Legend: ቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ "Saint Michael". [ማርያም፡] ምስለ፡ ፍቁር፡ ወልዳ፡ "[Mary] with her beloved Son". ቅዱስ፡ ወገብርኤል፡ "and Gabriel". 
 <note>The
                        miniature might have been produced for this Ms., but was added later
                        (legends are written by the scribe <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10788WaldaMuse">Walda Muse</persName>?).</note></decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
